# Glue Interview Prep — Concepts & Design Reference

**Purpose:** Study Glue and file-based ETL concepts using the **documented** file-processing-workflow design in this repo. Use this to understand how Glue fits, how ETL works in such a flow, and how to answer technical questions accurately.

**How to use this doc (honestly):**  
This material describes a **design/architecture** (Agency Lending – Equilend style) that is documented in this repo. It is **concept and reference prep**—so you can speak accurately about Glue, ETL, validation, DPUs, job args, etc. **Do not claim you built or operated this pipeline.** You can say you’ve studied this type of architecture and Glue, and that you have Spark foundations; then use these concepts to answer “what is Glue?”, “how would you design validation?”, “ETL vs ELT?”, etc.

